# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Private prompts: 
#   1. Drop in a folder named private/
#   2. Name the file  *.private.md (or .txt, .pdf, .docx, .xlsx, .pptx)
# Both are ignored automatically.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
private/
*.private.md
*.private.txt
*.private.pdf
*.private.docx
*.private.xlsx
*.private.pptx
